Micro service name : auth_service
                    
Checks if a username and password are correct and if so gives back a token like a digital pass 

We're using Flask- light weight web framework in python for creating API's 
            JWT(JSON Web Token) - Securly transmit user identity between client and server 

This service will handle where users send their username password and if the credentials are valid then we genearte a JWT token 
that token can be used for accessing other secure endpoints 

